# Home page section titles

On **`HomePage`**, every **`SectionHeader`** for main content rails (e.g. Memories, Greetings, Trending photo looks, Photos) must be **left-aligned**.

## Requirements

1. Do **not** pass **`titleAlign="center"`** on those headers. Omit **`titleAlign`** so the default **`start`** (left) alignment from **`SectionHeader`** applies.
2. If a new section is added on the home scroll with **`SectionHeader`**, keep the same pattern unless product explicitly requests centered headings for that block.

Other screens may still use **`titleAlign="center"`** when the design calls for it.
